OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fthis evening with showers merging into
OL,7,Flonger spells of rain overnight. This
OL,8,Fcould turn heavy at times. A chance of
OL,9,Fsome clear spells towards the far
OL,10,Fsouth of the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with spells
OL,13,Fof rain, this heavy at times. The rain
OL,14,Fwill turn showery into the afternoon
OL,15,Fso many areas will see some drier
OL,16,Fspells. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
