OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBrighter
OL,6,Fbut cooler on Sunday, with a cold
OL,7,Fnight following. Staying cool early
OL,8,Fnext week, with some further spells of
OL,9,Frain but also some sunshine at times.
